com.hazelcast.spi

Interface LiveOperations

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CallsPerMember

    public interface LiveOperations
    InvocationMonitor passes instances of this type to each LiveOperationsTracker so it can contribute the call IDs of invocations it is responsible for. The object is not thread-safe and is recycled.
